                     <interp inst="t18440304-929-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> steal<lb></lb>ing 39lbs. weight of lead, value 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440304-name-590" type="victimName">
